subject: CPMS
name: Intro to Clin Phys & Mov Sci
fullname: Introduction to Clinical Physiology and Movement Science
info: Overview of clinical physiology and clinical movement science. For students in such diverse fields as bioengineering, kinesiology, neuroscience, physical therapy, physiology, psychology, public health, occupational therapy.

subject: CPMS
name: Clinical Physiology Colloquium
fullname: Colloquium in Clinical Physiology and Movement Science
info:
Interdisciplinary course meets 1st and 3rd week of the month. Current research areas, scientific methods, and interpretation of results in the areas of clinical movement science and clinical physiology.

prereq: Undergrad level in basic anatomy and physiology is highly recommended
